step_data.thought: We have focused on the textbox labeled 'Group:' which can be used for filtering. Now, we need to fill this textbox with the ID or name that the user wants to filter by. Since no specific ID or name was provided in the instructions, let's assume the user wants to filter by the group name 'Wholesale'. We will enter this value into the textbox and then click the 'Search' button to apply the filter.
